{"tid":1354581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每區都成立自衛隊，護送街坊返屋企，點睇？","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:34:24.000Z","uid":83936,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"70a5dcf835b7b61a87970597496015fc1ba88558","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"18區都自發設立20~30人小隊<br />\n專守喺天橋，隧道，總之係啲放工落車必經之地<br />\n唔洗有政治成分，可能只係舉下牌，表達保護街坊嘅訊息<br />\n<br />\n同時帶出黑警/政府已經唔可信嘅意識形態<br />\n拉攏一啲中立或者中立偏藍嘅人，大家一家人嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n就算佢係乜政見都好，唔好同街坊嘈，只提出「我地唔係咩黃絲藍絲，大家咩立場都好，最近發生嘅事真係人神共憤，警察咁樣包庇黑社會，街坊嘅安全真係受到威脅㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n盡量用親和力去感染佢，如果佢開始認同黑警同政府唔可信嘅時候，其實佢已經漸漸企喺我地呢邊！<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗"},{"pid":"050f045c010d216543afa52bc2f40ceceb88229d","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2754adb13678eb0f9a220d99b356be84b2e9a8a","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"697331373bcbd5d6d341afbcb0e1fa2271822f69","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3023d89ed8a1f07d1263ed936b307bd5e27854e5","tid":1354581,"uid":277441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21097c460ac8f57680182e539566c5b8e2fbabdf","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"14bebbccfc0f60e47f3b3c58e154071f0bdded3a","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6b0f1b506c3abad49cc7c5fe4b431cf7ccd15cf6","tid":1354581,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7cf3ee145a3d7f021bc8b746aed23299adb3b301","tid":1354581,"uid":276457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB